                Refer to section 7.1.3.3
                of the e-Discharge_Summary_CDA_Implementation_Guide_v3.4.</report>
            <!-- Update Ended - Mantis Id 3038 -->

            <report test="count(cda:code[@code='101.20021'])> 1">Error:
